data.description: Discover luxury living in PGA Verano, Port St. Lucie, with this elegant 2-bedroom + den, 2-bath home, spanning 1,646 sq ft. Revel in the sophistication of tile floors across main living areas.  Experience the convenience of soft-close cabinets & drawers in the kitchen & master bath. The quartz countertops in the kitchen & baths add a touch of elegance, complemented by marble window sills throughout the home. The 10' tray ceilings in the living room & master bedroom elevate the home's grandeur. Indulge in the spa-like master shower, boasting floor-to-ceiling tiles. Ceiling fans throughout ensure comfort.  Let's not forget the screened porch out back.  CBS Construction with hurricane rated impact doors & windows will ensure affordable insurance rates.    See ''more'' for additional details. Situated adjacent to the renowned 54-hole PGA Golf Club with cart path access, your new home is more than a residenceit's a lifestyle!.  The 40,000 sq ft clubhouse and fitness center are at your fingertips, along with an indoor lap pool, 5 Har-Tru Hydro Tennis Courts, 27 Pickleball Courts, a resistance pool, and a 7000 sq ft E-Gym. Enjoy leisurely afternoons in the bocce court, card room, ballroom, or the demo kitchen. Relax in the saunas or unwind by the outdoor resort pool with cabanas. A convenient Publix is located by the front gate, adding to the ease of living in this exclusive community.
